---
title: Chicken Breast and Spinach Curry with Basmati Rice and Mango Chutney
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chicken Breast and Spinach Curry in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220906_R16_W42_UK_QR3939-26_KB_Main_swap_low-a3603581.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chicken-and-spinach-curry-chicken-breast-and-spinach-curry-62ff97fd8a28a1239a4e7da4-69b699ce.pdf
author: HelloFresh
